ygData.messageBody:
Had a lot, Xakeria, Xakery, Xaknafim, Zaknafim, Gog, Mongo. Grog was fun I
was an Ogre warrior and during the back up for the first Pwipe I died 7
times until it dawned on the GM that I could not come to the save point
because of the guards :). Luckily the Qeynos newbie area was the entire
world so I didn't have far to travel.
